\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"the lines\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 745}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport's biggest names\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 801}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 817}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles' beam performance\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"as she fell off before he sounded rather shell-shocked when he had to deliver her score: \\\"Well, it just wasn't to be!\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her score\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"C'est la vie for Simone on beam.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"C'est\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1121}, {\"ngram\": \"la vie\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1128}, {\"ngram\": \"Simone\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"beam\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh, my word.\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Oh, my word\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, that -\\\" Baker continued before abruptly stopping himself to listen in to Biles' complaints to her coaching team.\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baker\", \"score\": 0.9993245576355604, \"rank\": 0.0006758948109511667, \"text\": \"Baker\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baker\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles' complaints\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"her coaching team\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's talking about the atmosphere, she's talking about people shushing - we have talked about it and the atmosphere in here is like a